ective of the subfund is to achieve capital appreciation through investment on a global basis including in emerging markets in a diversified portfolio of investments as set out below odey asset management llp capita cf odey continental european cap gb gbp   low the investment objective of this fund is to achieve long term capital appreciation through investing primarily in quoted securities issued by companies with principal offices in continental europe and the normal policy of the fund is to invest in a broad spread of equities but the fund may also invest in government bonds other fixed interest securities and preferred stocks if in the opinion of the manager and the investment manager this is appropriate to the goal of maximising capital growth     bibey post   trending stock news penny stock news market news stock news latest headlines great elm capital corp gecc analysts see  eps second curve capital has upped by  million its qcr holdings qcrh position test analysts expect great elm capital corp nasdaqgecc to report  eps on august  after the closegecc’s profit would be m giving it  pe if the  eps is correct after having  more… eps for envestnet env expected at   analysts bullish atlas copco ab adr atlky stephen andrade among  analysts covering atlas copco ab otcmktsatlky  have buy rating  sell and  hold therefore  are positive atlas copco ab had  analyst reports since august   according to sratingsintel more… analysts see  eps for global eagle entertainment ent epoch investment partners raised jones lang lasalle jll holding winifred garcia analysts expect global eagle entertainment inc nasdaqent to report  eps on august they anticipate  eps change or  from last quarter’s  eps about  shares traded global more… analysts see  eps for bioscrip bios bank of commerce holdings has  sentiment eps for amplify snack brands betr expected at  mplx lp mplx si increased by  ack asset management has boosted its headwaters hw stake finemark national bank  trust trimmed mohawk